    "By the proposed generation method, a large number of foreign body intrusion data totaling 4000 sheets were obtained, and some samples are shown in Fig. 4.",
    "Image synthesis based approach.",
    "Manually attaching foreign objects to the background image is an effective method, which allows acquiring foreign object data in a specified scene, but has the following limitations for large-scale images.",
